<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">هـ ر م:</span> <span class="c2">(الْهَرَمُ)</span> كِبَرُ السِّنِّ وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(هَرِمَ)</span> مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(هَرِمٌ)</span> ، وَقَوْمٌ <span class="c2">(هَرْمَى)</span> . وَتَرْكُ الْعَشَاءِ <span class="c2">(مَهْرَمَةٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الْهَرَمَانِ)</span> بِنَاءٌ بِمِصْرَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>